00:00:14.460 --> 00:00:17.599
First is a lack of knowledge of the correct
principals.

00:00:17.599 --> 00:00:22.509
Second is a lack of knowledge of the correct
practices and jump techniques.

00:00:22.509 --> 00:00:27.749
